Class MediaItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orm.SugarRecord
      • it.polimi.dima.mediatracker.model.MediaItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sectioned, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Book, Movie, TVShow, Videogame

    public abstract class MediaItem
extends com.orm.SugarRecord
implements java.io.Serializable, Sectioned
    A generic media item, contains all properties common to all its implementations (e.g. title) It's a SugarRecord implementation: the external library Sugar ORM takes care of the database table automatically
